---
/**
 * Manifesto: Full-width pull quote / statement section.
 * Replaces Newsletter as the emotional closer before the footer.
 */
---

<section class="py-32 border-t border-border-subtle">
  <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6 text-center">
    <div class="i-ph-quotes text-5xl text-secondary/30 mx-auto mb-8"></div>

    <blockquote
      class="text-3xl md:text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-display font-bold text-primary leading-tight mb-10"
    >
      "No hay un solo centímetro cuadrado en todo el dominio de nuestra
      existencia humana sobre el cual Cristo, que es
      <span class="italic font-serif text-secondary">Soberano sobre todo</span>,
      no grite: &laquo;¡Mío!&raquo;"
    </blockquote>

    <footer class="text-sm text-text-muted font-mono uppercase tracking-widest">
      — Abraham Kuyper (1880)
    </footer>

    <div class="mt-12">
      <a
        href="/about"
        class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-sm font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-text-muted hover:text-secondary transition-colors"
      >
        Leer el manifiesto
        <div class="i-ph-arrow-right"></div>
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
